{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-20229/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-20229"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["2:02:29"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman pushes a stroller while sitting on a park bench."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-20229","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-20229"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1/eb954b90-be08-4e61-9c8e-e4b1e61cc276","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:37:19.273Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In Alma’s vision of their future, the couple leave their baby in Cyril’s care. Her fantasy of their life together still includes the strange familial dynamics at play in Reynolds’s household. As Cyril was his partner in running the House of Woodcock, she will also be a part of raising their child, maintaining her motherly role.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:376.38755980861015,139.44078947368408,555.9061004784687,482.6555023923444"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1/18793a27-57e4-4c4e-94d6-4f3611d363dd","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:37:41.508Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Given their past and Cyril’s personality, it seems unlikely that Reynolds’s sister would take on this role of caretaker to the couple’s child—another indicator that this vision is simply what Alma wishes for. Symbolically, though, this sight gestures toward what Reynolds has been looking for: a replacement mother figure.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20229/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:999.1372607655483,389.13427033492803,914.2718301435398,676.5699760765549"}}}]}]}]}